items.name: Mario Kart (Wii)
items.shortDescription: Mario Kart Wii features 16 new tracks, as well as 16 retro tracks from previous Mario Kart games. Dozens of characters from the Mushroom Kingdom are present, and each has his or her own collection of customized vehicles to race. For the first time in the Mario Kart series, racers can compete on either motorbikes or karts as they find shortcuts, grab power-ups and take down other racers in a frantic free-for-all. Four people can compete on a single Wii system, or up to 12 people near or far can race and battle via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection, Nintendo's online gaming service.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Worldwide Racing: Play with up to three friends locally or challenge up to 11 friends via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection in the biggest Mario Kart race yet! All tracks and modes of play are available for online races.</li><li>Mario Kart Channel: Visit the Mario Kart Channel on your Wii Menu to check regional and worldwide stats, friend rankings, download ghost data, participate in worldwide Time Trial events, and more!</li><li>New Wheels and Courses: cruise brand-new tracks and arenas, or enjoy a blast from the past going fender-to-fender on one of the classics. Tired of riding on four wheels? Bust out one of the all-new motorbikes for special tricks and techniques.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Comic Mischief</li></ul>

items.name: New Super Mario Bros. (Wii)
items.shortDescription: A classic 2D adventure, the game follows the style of New Super Mario Bros. for Nintendo DS. Princess Peach has been kidnapped by Bowser and it's up to Mario to save her, but this time he's not alone! Up to four players can join in the fun at the same time, playing as Mario, Luigi or either one of two Toads. Jump, swim and fly through eight classically-themed worlds, with even more challenges awaiting the best players. New power-ups such as the Propeller Suit and Penguin Suit grant unique abilities to traverse levels and combat Koopas, and the return of Yoshi guarentees an enemy-gobbling good time for all. New Super Mario Bros. Wii is also the first Nintendo game to feature a dynamic help system, which allows you to access a mode which allows you to watch how a level can be completed if you are stuck.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>New Super Mario Bros. Wii offers a combination of cooperation and competition. Players can pick each other up to save them from danger or toss them into it.</li><li>Mario, Luigi and two Toads are all playable characters, while many others from the Mushroom Kingdom make appearances throughout the game. Players can even ride different Yoshi characters and use their tongues to swallow enemies, items and even balls of fire.</li><li>In some areas, players use the motion abilities of the Wii Remote controller. The first player to reach a seesaw might make it tilt to help his or her character reach a higher platform - or might make it tilt incorrectly just to mess with other players.</li><li>New items include the propeller suit, which will shoot players high into the sky with just a shake of the Wii Remote, and Mario's new ability to transform into Penguin Mario.</li><li>At the end of each stage during the coin battle multiplayer mode, players are ranked based on the number of coins they have collected.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Comic Mischief</li></ul>

items.name: Nintendo Wii Nunchuk Controller - Black (Wii)
items.shortDescription: Connect the Nintendo Wii Nunchuk Controller to the Wii Remote and get ready. You've just begun a journey into the most immersive, heated gameplay experience ever offered. This combo of Nintendo Wii Nunchuk Controller offers the utmost precision. The Nunchuk controller and the accelerometer contained within it are the next leap in gaming. In first-person shooters, the Wii Nunchuck controller carries the burden of movement, freeing you to aim and fire using a more natural motion with the Wii Remote. In a football game, you can make your quarterback elusive with the Nunchuk controller while you look for an open receiver to throw to using the Wii Remote. Nintendo's Wii Nunchuck controller was the first add-on released for the wildly popular and innovate Wii Remote. The Nintendo Nunchuk Controller lets you guide character movements on the screen with a simple analog joystick while handling your own hand and body movements with the Wii Remote.
items.longDescription: <b>Nintendo Wii Nunchuk Controller (Wii):</b><br><ul><li>Connect to Wii Remote</li><li>Carries the burden of movement</li><li>Use the Nintendo Wii Controller - Black (Wii) with first-person shooters and sports games</li><li>Color: Black</li></ul>

items.name: Your Shape (Wii)
items.shortDescription: The game starts with a scan of your body: for the first time ever, you appear on screen and receive a full body diagnosis. Based on your specific diagnosis, the game is able to recommend the program best suited to your body shape and fitness level, to which you can also add your own priorities and preferences. Finally, as an exercise program only works if you do it right, Your Shape's unique Body Tracking Technology follows your every move in real time, so that each minute invested is effective in helping you obtain your ideal body shape.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Unique camera tracking technology.</li><li>Unique diagnosis:</li><li>A scan of your body.</li><li>A detailed analysis of your overall body shape and your fitness level.</li><li>A customised training program, to which you can add your personal priorities.</li><li>Unique tracking of your movements:</li><li>Real time feedback on quality of execution of your movements.</li><li>Precise assessment of the efficiency of your workout.</li><li>Playful and stimulating mindset that keeps you motivated as you are guided through each movement by a coach.</li><li>Coach next to you, giving you the motivational pep talks to keep you on track.</li><li>Fun signs and feedbacks, encouraging you to go beyond your limits.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE</li></ul>

items.name: My Amusement Park and Digging for Dinosaurs Game Pack (DS)
items.shortDescription: Build and manage your very own amusement park! Travel on expeditions to unearth dinosaurs!
items.longDescription: <ul><li>My Amusement Park:</li><li>Make it your own - Choose from four different theme park plans and then build it - from its rides, attractions, landscaping, decorations and more!</li><li>8 Logic & Puzzle Games - Play games to earn more money for a bigger, better park featuring larger and more expensive rides and attractions.</li><li>Keep Customers Happy - Fix broken rides, fulfill food orders, clear parking jams and more as you tend to customers and grow your park into a huge success.</li><li>Digging for Dinosaurs:</li><li>Dinosaur Facts - Separate fact from myth as you unearth 21 different dinosaurs like Tyrannosaurus Rex, Brachiosaurus and Microraptor!</li><li>Eight Dinosaur Games - Battle dinosaurs, scavenge for food and more while playing games that show how dinosaurs survive in the wild.</li><li>Digging Adventures - Play games to earn points for dinosaur digs and then rebuild the dinosaur bones you find to display in the Hall of Dinosaurs!</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE</li></ul>

items.name: Super Smash Brothers (Wii U)
items.shortDescription: A Smashing Good Time! Mario! Link! Samus! Pikachu! All of your favorite Nintendo characters are back, along with plenty of new faces, in Super Smash Bros. for Wii U, the next entry in the beloved Super Smash Bros. series. Up to four players can battle each other locally or online across beautifully designed stages inspired by classic Nintendo home console games. With a variety of control options and amiibo compatibility, the timeless Super Smash Bros. battles come alive.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Compete with classic players from the Super Smash Bros. series, along with new challengers like Mega Man, Little Mac or newly announced Palutena, the Goddess of Light from the Kid Icarus games. For the first time, players can even compete as their own Mii characters.</li><li>Use a variety of control methods during the high-energy and action-filled battles, including Nintendo GameCube controllers - the longtime controller of choice for hard-core Super Smash Bros. players.</li><li>Customize move sets when playing locally or online with friends.</li><li>Connect with amiibo for added fun.</li><li>Experience the beauty of Super Smash Bros. for Wii U in stunning HD, a first for the series.</li><li>Fight against friends and family locally or online, or battle random challengers from all over the world online in "For Fun" or "For Glory" modes.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE 10+ with Comic Mischief, Mild Suggestive Themes, and Cartoon Violence</li></ul>

items.name: Mario Kart 8 (Wii U)
items.shortDescription: For the first time in HD, Nintendo's Mario Kart franchise comes to the Wii U console, introducing new racing circuit designs and antigravity karts that will have players driving upside down. Players will also enjoy a variety of series-favorite features, including the return of 12-player online competitive play, hang-gliders, underwater racing and motorbikes.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>The new antigravity feature allows for never-imagined racing circuit designs. Players will speed through courses and find themselves suddenly racing on walls in a hanted mansion or upside-down over Princess Peach's Castle as their wheels automatically rotate and shift into antigravity gear.</li><li>Mario Kart TV lets players share highlight videos they submitted to Miiverse.</li><li>Experience a wealth of features that span the series, including 12-player online competitive play. Elements first introduced in Mario Kart 7, such as hang gliders and underwater racing, along with elements introduced in Mario Kart Wii, such as motorbikes and performing tricks in midair, also make their return.</li><li>Fan-favorites Waluigi and Toadette re-join the cast of familiar characters from the Mushroom Kingdom.</li><li>Crisp HD graphics and a 60-frames-per-second frame rate offer players the most visually stunning entry in the series yet.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Comic Mischief</li></ul>

items.name: Super Mario 3D World - Nintendo Selects (Wii U)
items.categoryPath: Video Games/Nintendo Wii U / Wii/Wii U Games
items.shortDescription: Nintendo Selects highlights a variety of great games at a great price, including this one. For the first time ever, Nintendo has created a four-player Mario game set in a 3D world. The game, developed by the same team that created Super Mario 3D Land for Nintendo 3DS and the Super Mario Galaxy games for Wii, lets up to four players play as Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach and Toad. Each character has his or her own unique characteristics, and people can play cooperatively or competitively. The new cat transformation turns characters into adorable felines that can scratch enemies and even scamper up the flagpole at the end of levels. Clear warp pipes add some new puzzle elements to game play.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Each chracter has unique abilities and play styles. For example, Princess Peach glides over gaps, while Luigi has his trademark extra-high jump.</li><li>The new cat transformation allows players to run on all fours, pounce on enemies, attack in midair or use their claws to scamper up walls and goal poles.</li><li>Explore colorful 3D environments filled with obstacles and contraptions like transparent pipes and vertical conveyor belts, which add new puzzle elements.</li><li>Use the Wii U GamePad controller's touch screen to search for hidden blocks and to freeze enemies in place.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Mild Cartoon Violence</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: <p>The Turtle Beach TBS-4256-01 Ear Force Marvel Super Heroes Disney Infinity Headset is an officially licensed product. It is specially designed to maximize your enjoyment for the upcoming, highly anticipated sequel to Disney Infinity and plays off the success of the Guardians of the Galaxy movie. Personalize it with any of the three Marvel character decals, including Iron Man, Black Widow and Guardians of the Galaxy. This stereo gaming headset features full-range sound, from supersonic highs to subterranean lows, to match the vast levels and incredible gameplay of Marvel Super Heroes. Powerful 50mm neodymium speakers, crystal-clear chat and a high-sensitivity microphone make online play into a heroic gaming event, especially in the game's bigger and better Toy Box mode. Other features include noise-isolating technology, adjustable audio and variable bass boost.</p>

items.name: Game Party 3 (Wii)
items.shortDescription: Game Party 3 brings casual gamers and families a fresh take on the popular Game Party franchise with a high-energy social gaming experience. Available exclusively on the Wii system, Game Party 3 incorporates brand new games and challenges along with a revamped variety of the franchise's classic favorites. Players compete in groups of up to 16, taking on new games such as Billiards, Mini Golf, Smack-a-Troll and Bocce Ball, as well as familiar favorites like Darts, Ping Cup, Trivia, and Horseshoes. Using the Wii's intuitive controller, all games are easily accessible to young and old, experienced and casual gamers alike. With 19 robust games and countless variations, there's something for everyone.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Experience Eight Brand New Games: For the first time play Billiards, Bumper Pool, Mini Golf, Smack-a-Troll, Bocce Ball, Racquetball, Croquet, and a remake of arcade classic Root Beer Tapper.</li><li>Enjoy 11 Updated Favorites: Revisit classic Game Party games with new layouts, levels and a robust database of challenging new trivia. Returning favorites include Darts, Hoop Shoot, Ping Cup, Shuffleboard, Skill Ball, Trivia, Puck Bowling, Horseshoes, Beanbags, QB Challenge and Lawn Darts.</li><li>Four-Player Action for All Games: Compete with up to four players simultaneously to see who brings their A" Game.</li><li>Compete in Tournament Mode: Arrange bracketed tournaments for up to sixteen players and discover the ultimate Game Party player in the group.</li><li>Customise Your Character: Create-a-Player mode allows everyone to create and customize unique character looks, and lets players choose to play left- or right-handed.</li><li>Personalised Player Profiles: Track personal high scores and earn game tickets, which can be used to unlock special in-game equipment and additional create-a-player attributes.</li><li>Compete in Six Unique Environments: Take on game challenges in the lounge, sports zone, family fun zone, rec room, backyard, or country club.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Violent References</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: Join an epic adventure with the Angry Birds in the legendary Star Wars universe, re-mastered for gaming systems! Use the Force, wield your Lightsaber, and blast away Pigtroopers on an intergalactic journey from the deserts of Tatooine to the depths of the Pig Star! Can you become a Jedi Master and restore freedom to the galaxy? May the birds be with you!

items.name: Just Dance 2015 (Wii)
items.shortDescription: Just Dance 2015 is the latest, most awesome-filled version of the world's #1 dance game, and is bringing new moves and game modes to over 40 top tracks. There are a million reasons to play and a million stories to be created with Just Dance 2015! With more than 50 million copies of Just Dance titles in homes around the world, our players are as important as ever, and the new features in Just Dance 2015 bring people together in more ways than ever before. For the first time ever, you too can be in the game. The all-new Community Remix feature puts players in the global spotlight by allowing them to become a Just Dance coach that players everywhere can dance along to. Just Dance 2015 also introduces Challenger mode where players will be able to compete against their past performances or challenge friends anywhere to beat their score, even if they can't play at the same time. Plus, this year we're bringing even more excitement to World Dance Floor, the online multiplayer mode.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Be a part of the game! With the all-new Community Remix feature, you can become a Just Dance coach who players everywhere can dance along to. With the camera on your console, record yourself dancing to a song and share in the game.</li><li>Never dance alone! In the new Challenger mode, you can dance against friends and family and top-ranked Just Dance players from around the world. The best part is you don't even have to play at the same time; you can play against previous performances and even share your score with the community!</li><li>Online multiplayer is back! World Dance Floor, the online multiplayer mode, lets you dance with anyone, anywhere in the world. Track your standing on the global leaderboard and check out other fun stats on other players from around the world.</li><li>Share your coolest dance moments! The upgraded Autodance feature records players while they're dancing to create short, funny, shareable videos. Autodance videos are now automatically generated while you're dancing, so you can instantly share it once the song is finished!</li><li>Just Dance favorites are back! Get in a workout by using Sweat mode to track the calories you're burning while dancing, or choose to own the spotlight in On Stage mode, where one player can dance and lead one or two backup dancers! items.name: Splatoon (Wii U)
items.shortDescription: Show Your True Colors. Splatter enemies and claim your turf as the ink-spewing, squid-like characters called Inklings in Nintendo's new third-person action shooter game for the Wii U console. Challenge your friends in chaotic four-on-four matches, in which the goal is to get your ink on as many places as possible and claim your turf, all while strategically submerging yourself in your team's colors and blasting your enemies. This is a colorful and chaotic online third-person action shooter - exclusively on Wii U.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Team up and take on other teams in an action-filled battle to cover the level with as much ink as possible. Spray walls to access hard-to-reach areas.</li><li>Covering more territory with ink unlocks powered-up super weapons that can be used to attack rivals or cover more turf.</li><li>Strategy is everything. Defeat enemies to splatter them in an explosion of ink, covering more turf for your team. But choose wisely: Players who only go after the enemy might find their turf redecorated in their enemies' colors.</li><li>Refill ink tanks, hide from opponents or move faster by turning into a squid and diving into the ink with the tap of a button.</li><li>Select between multiple control options on the Wii U GamePad controller, including using gyroscopic controls to look around, allowing for better aiming and control.</li><li>Hop online and battle in four-on-four matches.</li><li>Broadband Internet access required for online play.</li><li>Additional accessories required for multiplayer mode; sold separately.</li><li>ESRB Rating: RATING PENDING</li></ul>
